Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.18,0:01:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there, boss kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't your kitty friends here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitties!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're headed to the café.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't look directly at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue-light-cutting glasses, equipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a wonderful café.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,With the AC running,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fallen Warrior over there \Nlooks nice and cool, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Fallen warrior?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny, that red scarf really suits you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you there, Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I've been neglecting the café!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like she can see all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:02:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Daiya-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she's not a magical girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She might be able to see us to some degree,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but I doubt she can hear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's extremely rare, but there are people
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,who can see us without meeting the \Nrequirements of a magical girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she can see {\i1}too{\i0} much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Fallen Warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've cooled down plenty,\N so you're ready to go back now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he went to Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny, please go to Heaven already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She feels a lot more \Nmagical girl-y than Chiya to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. At the very least, I don't feel \Nlike she has any ill intentions towards us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about I help you\Ntwo ascend to Heaven next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:03:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To be continued.
